Description: Replication package for "Selection Bias on Justifiable
    Homicide Reports". This package provides datasets and functions to 
    reproduce the analysis examining the association between race and gender and 
    justifiable homicides data from the Supplementary Homicides Reports (SHR). 
    Includes state and fips-level data from 1976-2023, regression and 
    modeling functions.
